spanGrp.span: Jina langu ka shule naitwa Gombanera
asees gad endan hij gad ebaranyeen
We are still here, we still have good relations with our neighbors
Sisi bado tupo huku bado tuna ujirani mwema
siid ar iwurj isiy gwaramags dahagi qwalas dahagi
If a person wrongs another, if they hit their friend
Mtu hata kama anamkosea mwingine, anampiga mwenzake
nyes seen qany eguraiiny hanan ab hij aa geyat jeed get gumd get aa geb ee
Often they are called to address complaints under the tree to go...
Huwa wanaitwa hapo na kupeleka malalamiko chini ya mti kwenda...
inyagan hanan siid da ramags gelaseew hanan njagood
If they are found to have wronged someone, they are given a fine
gabalool gwalanyeek aa gelaseew njagood siid dita aa geyamu
The elders will speak and give them a fine, and they will say
Wataongea wazee na watampiga faini yule mtu na watasema
geyat kwa mwenyekiti wa kitongoji iwurj gil goshindikan kwa mwenyekiti wa kitongoji
They will be sent to the chairperson of the neighborhood, if they don't succeed with the chairperson
Atapelekwa kwa menyekiti wa kitogoji akishindokana kwa mwenyekiti wa kitongoji
geyat ofiain iyashindikan ab ofaiin geyat mahakamani
They will be sent to the office, if they don't succed at the office they will be sent to the court
Atapelekwa ofsini akishindikana ifisini watampeleka mahakamani
siini gidil asimjeeg alakini eed haw aa medili
This person has failed with the Asimjeeg, but in the big picture we haven't failed
Huyo mtu ameshindikana kwa waasimjeega lakini sehemu kubwa hatukushindwa
ar qamn iramags surja nyas seen geyamanan jeed quwa hij aa gepalool
Even now if you wrong your friend often them are brought home to be questioned
Hata sasa wakimkosea mwingine huwa wanamleta nyumbani na kumhoji
They will be warned right then
ar iwurj orjeed aa godil giyeet aa sagarmood
Even if a person has wronged their wife
Hata kama jamaa amekoseana na mke wake
gigobiit hanan gwarugsiiny kwanza qany egursiin ukooed dita
They will be advised first or will be called by their clan
Atakaa kushauriana kwanza au kuitwa ile ukoo wao
au kabireed manung' eyata gumd get gurgwageed
Or before being sent to the meeting under the tree
Au kabla hajapelekwa kwenye kikao chini ya mti
He will go to the elders
His father, and he will be asked
jaft ind majiil gewi gwan qooni
A child hasn't given birth to themselves, there is his father
aa gwand qamat gijepars siis da jili jaft dit ba
And his mother, he will be asked who gave birth to him
Na kuna mam yake atauluzwa yule aliyemzaa
gigabalool hanan ab howa ni wurj gwaramags gwargweedan aa gigopalool aa gwayeesh obigd quwar
They will talk there, that person who wronged their partner, and they will talk and say "Return to your home"
Wataongea pale huyo aliyemkosea mme wake nawataongea na kuwaambia mrudi nyumbani kwenu
These things will stop if they fail
He will be sent below the tree
They will invite the elders and talk
He will be given a fine
siid imud da ramags dahagi gabigd qareedany
If there's a person who wronged their friend, he will return to his home
Kama kuna mtu aliyemkosea mwenzake atarudi nyumbani kwake
asees ng'asheeg su ba batakin aa qo qamn
These things of prosecution, until today
Sisi hayo mambo hayo ya mashitaka mpaka leo
yaani ahang'ony siid gicha go goshtak ab mahakaman
That is, it's hard for a person to go to be prosecuted in the court
Yaani ni ngumu mtu kwenda kushitaki mahakamani
We are still participating in this
gwawurj gil siy buneed gwand ar ng'ashand ja gwasin qadoowonangvwak gad gabaranyi
And if there is still faith, people still understand each other and share
Ni kama ikiwepo na ibada watu bado wanaelewana wanashirikiana
yaani ng'asheeg seen gad endan ng'asheeg ed jadi
That is, we still have all of these things, and the traditional things
Yaani sisi kwa mambo yote bado tupo na mambo ya jadi
mandan gidab nyas seen gijang'een hiji
There is no question of where you will start
And you send the person directly to the office
mpak kwanz qany ebalool asees asimjeeg
First we Asimjeeg need to talk about it first
ar qamn gad ebarandosch asimjeeg manung' ejagd giyeet
Even now we Asimjeeg haven't grown apart
If there is something I have done wrong, you will ask me
Kama kuna jambo nitakosea mtaniuliza nyingine
ng'asheeg ga ng'adonng'wak gelulay giyeet ar da dugwa qamn
Often for farming we ask each other to help, even if it is farming with cattle
Sisi kwa mambo ya kilimo huwa tunaalikana misaada hata wa kilimo cha dume
qay mendawiini dugw qamn aa qonyas buneed dugw
In the old days there weren't any cattle, but now people have gotten cattle
'Zamani hatukuwa na ng''ombe lakini sasa watu wamepata ng''ombe'
nyas seen gelulj giyeet abij buneeda
hekajeeg gwach ar ayiyeeny au ginadaw hekajeeg ar muut
Even if it's two acres or if there are five acres
Ekari hata kama ni mbili au una ekari tano
gijaluul buneed seen asimjeeg sendsend aa abij aa qofk aa gang'adisch
You will invite all of the Asimjeeg, they will come to farm
Utawaalika watu wote waasimjega wote watakuja kulima
ukweed gigoshal ar ab awechand akalele gijeeny qana mboyd au buneed isang' diya
The field will be done on that very day if there are a lot of people
Shamba litaisha siku ileile kama watu ni wengi
We help each other a lot
gejaqwadeas nyas gekulij aa geway masayd
If our cattle are being stolen, we sound the alarm and go to follow them
'Tukiibiwa ng''ombe tunapiga yowe na kwenda kufuatilia'
irikusud eb eweed siid dit eyamn alanjeed gik sijagwatin
If we are lucky we'll help the person to return their livestock that were stolen
lli kusudi tukamsaidie yule mtu turudishe mifugo yaliyoibwa
ii dugw gili au ii jambas siid seen gwasayiin
If it's cattle or the person is a bandit, it's like this, too
'Kama ni ng''ombe au mtu ni jambazi ni hivyo pia'
